Title: Part 7: Amon Hen
Text:
I followed the shore until I came across a small camp, but instead of the fellowship there were only Uruk-Hai.
I should fight my way free. Boromir was traveling alone, he needs our help! Maybe it's not too late..
CompleteText:
I'm late, a group of Uruk-Hai is already here and there's no sign of the fallowship.
I should keep following the path.

(The Horn of Gondor sounds in the distance!)
Boromir must be here somewhere, I hear his horn in the distance.
